DESCRIPTION:<p dir="ltr"><i>Two days\, more than thirty-five films from aro
 und the world by noteworthy filmmakers\, one awesome community for film dis
 covery</i></p><p dir="ltr">This is BIFF’s mission: to scour the world for f
 antastic short- and longform films and exhibit a highly curated collection 
 of the best contemporary works from filmmakers all across the globe. It’s a
  celebration of cinematic imagination\, right here in Bloomington\, Indiana
 . But on Thursday the 3rd of April\, BIFF will be featuring the Student fil
 m talent from Bloomington and Indiana at Redbud Books to kick off BIFFs fou
 rth year. </p><p>For more information\, visit the website: <a href="https:/
 /www.biff-bloom.com/2025-student-film-showcase">https://www.biff-bloom.com/
 2025-student-film-showcase</a></p>
