UID:23ulj1orb2ev6b2c8comhr5rqi@google.com
CREATED:20260329T203217Z
DESCRIPTION:Creative Resolve: The Future of Global Health follows the harro
 wing stories of leading Global health experts and activists in their fight 
 to expand access to essential medicines. It showcases stories of resilience
 \, such as the fight against HIV in Rwanda\, AIDS activism\, and the eradic
 ation of smallpox\, showing how collaboration and creative solutions have l
 ed to major strides in global health. Creative Resolve emphasizes the impor
 tance of expanding access to essential medicines\, investing in prevention\
 , and strengthening global health systems.
LAST-MODIFIED:20260329T203218Z
LOCATION:Redbud Books\, 408 W Kirkwood Ave\, Bloomington\, IN 47404\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Creative Resolve: Creating the Future We Want - a Film Screening
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
