CREATED:20250903T104803Z
DESCRIPTION:Please join us for September's play reading\, The Pigpen by Gol
 sa Sohrabi\, an MFA candidate in playwriting at IU! The reading will be on 
 September 12th at 7:30 at Redbud Books.\n\nKamand and Behrouz\, a couple gr
 appling with economic challenges\, decide to rent one of their rooms to Elh
 am\, a friend of Kamand's. Elham\, an experienced traveler through Couchsur
 fing\, plans for a brief stay at their place between her journeys. However\
 , her short-term arrangement transforms into a permanent residency. \n\nThe
  Redbud Community Play Reading Series is a free monthly reading series in w
 hich community members and theatre professionals share in the joy of readin
 g plays aloud together. These unrehearsed readings offer opportunities to a
 ppreciate plays written by local playwrights and IU alums\, and established
  plays we may not otherwise be exposed to.
LAST-MODIFIED:20250903T104803Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:September Play Reading: The Pigpen by Golsa Sohrabi
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
