DESCRIPTION:In memory of Peter Watkins\, who passed away recently\, we are 
 showing his extended film <i>La Commune</i>.<br><br><i>La Commune</i> tells
  the story of the Paris Commune\, a French revolutionary government that se
 ized power in Paris on 18 March 1871 after the defeat of Napoleon III.<br><
 br>The following day\, Sunday 11/9 at 6pm\, we'll have a discussion of the 
 film and the ideas explored there.
