UID:607j1p1ldk3ti030897rmb1fai@google.com
CREATED:20250108T035205Z
DESCRIPTION:Stay tuned for a new date for this screening\, in April \n\n"Th
 e Young Girls of Rochefort" unfolds in the charming coastal town of Rochefo
 rt\, where twin sisters Delphine and Solange\, a dance and music teacher re
 spectively\, dream of escaping their humdrum lives and finding true love. A
 s a lively traveling fair arrives\, the town becomes a stage for romantic e
 ntanglements and missed connections. Delphine and Solange\, each longing fo
 r their ideal partners\, find their desires intertwined with the romantic p
 ursuits of other townspeople\, including Maxence\, a sailor and painter sea
 rching for his perfect woman\, and their mother Yvonne\, who runs a local c
 afe. The film dances through a weekend of colorful musical numbers and vibr
 ant set designs\, illustrating the whimsical yet poignant search for love a
 nd fulfillment. Through a series of chance encounters and near misses\, the
  characters navigate the complexities of romance\, highlighting themes of f
 ate\, destiny\, and the pursuit of dreams\, all wrapped in a lighthearted\,
  optimistic\, and visually captivating cinematic experience.  \n\nOur secre
 t screening series brings together an eclectic assortment of films chosen b
 y the film programming team based on their own interests and desires.
LAST-MODIFIED:20250315T123903Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:(RESCHEDULED) Secret Screening: The Young Girls of Rochefort
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
