DESCRIPTION:In our first year\, we planted 2666 trees! Come by and pick up 
 some free trees outside of Redbud Books. Courtesy of the Neighborhood Plant
 ing Project and the Center for Sustainable Living     \n\nRedbud Books part
 ners with the Neighborhood Planting Project to plant one tree for every boo
 k we sell. \nSince 2017\, the NPP has distributed more than 117\,000 free n
 ative fruit and nut trees to our neighbors in order to build food autonomy\
 , mitigate local effects of climate change\, and make Bloomington a more be
 autiful place.\n\nWe will have hawthorn\, hazelnut\, elderberry\, redbud\, 
 buttonbush\, pecan\, pawpaw trees available.
LAST-MODIFIED:20250401T131800Z
LOCATION:Redbud Books\, 408 W Kirkwood Ave\, Bloomington\, IN 47404\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Neighborhood Planting Project Tree Giveaway
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
