 ut its hopes haunt our past. Reading revolutionary history from the Paris C
 ommune to the George Floyd Uprising by the light of communist theory\, from
  Marx to C. L. R. James\, The Future of Revolution illuminates the possibil
 ities for overcoming class society in the twenty-first century.
