DESCRIPTION:Coming up\, on March 26\, author Oliver Haimson will be joined 
 by Meredith Lee to talk about his new book\, <i>Trans Technologies.</i><br>
 <br><i>Trans Technologies</i> examines the growing world of technologies th
 at address the unique needs and challenges faced by transgender people. Dra
 wing from in-depth interviews with creators of over 100 trans technologies—
 including apps\, games\, health resources\, virtual reality systems\, and m
 ore—the book explores the power and limits of this exploding technological 
 movement and emphasizes the crucial role of community in driving social cha
 nge.
LAST-MODIFIED:20250321T231933Z
LOCATION:Redbud Books\, 408 W Kirkwood Ave\, Bloomington\, IN 47404\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Trans Technologies author talk and Q&A
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
