CREATED:20241202T120514Z
DESCRIPTION:The Creative Cafe is a monthly series inspired by three main ob
 jectives: \n\n1.  A desire to have dedicated spaces to honoring new residen
 ts and artists through performance and dialogue. \n2. A place for all artis
 ts within Bloomington to socialize and invent new means of collaboration an
 d expression. \n3. Time and space of proactive community-planning and desti
 gmatized conversations around migration in a country that has seen an overw
 helming increase in xenophobia and anti-migrant sentiment. \n\nDuring this 
 time creative time\, we invite you are able to meet someone new\, hear some
  amazing performers\, and strategize ways in which we as an artistic commun
 ity can prioritize performers and spaces that highlight conversations and l
 ived experiences of migration
LAST-MODIFIED:20241202T120514Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Creative Cafe
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
