DESCRIPTION:A long-term\, hybrid in-person and online reading group in memo
 ry of our beloved friend\, Joshua Clover inspired by Joshua’s understanding
  of communism\, and social transformation. \n\nOur itinerary begins with Ri
 ot Strike Riot (Clover) and works backward through Chaos and Governance in 
 the Modern World System (Arrighi and silver )\, The Eclipse And Re-emergenc
 e Of The Communist Movement(Dauvé and Martin)\, The Arcana Of Reproduction 
 (Fortunati\, Trans Austin and Colantuono)\, Notes On Dialectics (James)\, C
 apital V I (Marx\, Trans Reitter or Fowkes) and then returns to the present
  for The Future of Revolution (Bernes). \n\nIf people agree the group will 
 be run as a discussion by rotating facilitators. It could last 18 months or
  so. We will begin Thursday\, September 11 at 7:30.
LAST-MODIFIED:20260102T020719Z
LOCATION:Redbud Books\, 408 W Kirkwood Ave\, Bloomington\, IN 47404\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Materialism Reading Group
TRANSP:OPAQUE
