DESCRIPTION:Join us for a talk with Monica Chen!\n\nMonica Chen\, is the ex
 ecutive director of New Roots Institute! She leads innovative educational p
 rograms that empower high school and college students to advocate for susta
 inable food systems and raise awareness about factory farming. Through focu
 sed regional efforts\, New Roots is changing attitudes toward plant-centere
 d menus.\n\nMonica also advises organizations like Scarlet Spark and has a 
 rich background in environmental education. She holds a BA from UC Berkeley
  and a Master's in Education from the University of New Mexico.
