DESCRIPTION:The Redbud Fiction Reading Group is a monthly reading group foc
 using on exciting recent literature that you might not have an opportunity 
 to read or discuss otherwise. Meetings generally happen near the end of the
  month\, on a Sunday\, and discussion is centered around the entire text. A
 ll are welcome to attend\, regardless of reading progress\, and the vibe is
  always fun and casual. If you have a book you would like to suggest and re
 ad\, or if you would like to facilitate a future group\, please feel free t
 o reach out to us at <a href="mailto:contact@redbudbooks.org" target="_blan
 k"><u>contact@redbudbooks.org</u></a>.
