DESCRIPTION:This container is devoted to connection- to ourselves\, to comm
 unity and to the earth. This circle is a sacred space to honor motherhood -
  as a teacher\, as a path to self discovery and a gateway to deepened prese
 nce. We will sit in a circle. I will bring a few cushions and blankets for 
 those that wish to be on the floor. There will be yummy snacks and tea/coff
 ee! Participants will need to bring a journal and pen. We will open the cir
 cle with a meditation and an introduction to our theme. There will be journ
 al prompts for reflection. Witnessing and sharing will be woven into the ci
 rcle time together.
