 ore diverse viewpoints\, methodologies\, and critical approaches within the
  field.</p><p>This year's conference\, scheduled for March 7-8\, will featu
 re keynote speakers Cory Doctorow and Ramon Resendiz. Our theme is "Media S
 tudies in/at/from the Margins."</p><br>For more information about the confe
 rence and schedule\, visit their website: <a href="https://mediaschool.indi
 ana.edu/student-portal/get-involved/common-ground/index.html">https://media
