UID:2iapbateng8p5a4fekugtjn075@google.com
CREATED:20250321T230945Z
DESCRIPTION:<p><b>To Make Big Tech Less Harmful\, Make it Less Important</b
 ></p><p>World governments spent the past 20 years passing laws designed to 
 make giant tech companies behave themselves. This was a catastrophic failur
 e. But the most consequential factor in the harms from Big Tech isn’t how b
 ad the companies are - it’s how INESCAPABLE they are. Policies that make Bi
 g Tech unimportant - policies that make it easy to leave Big Tech\, and tha
 t eliminate tech’s role as gatekeeper - will hit Big Tech right where it hu
 rts\, square in the dongle\, making tech less powerful\, more biddable\, an
 d\, most importantly\, less relevant.</p><br>More information here: <a href
 ="https://events.iu.edu/ostromworkshop/event/1843316-hls-beyond-the-web-cor
 y-doctorow">https://events.iu.edu/ostromworkshop/event/1843316-hls-beyond-t
 he-web-cory-doctorow</a><br><br>Part of the <span>2024-25 Beyond the Web Sp
 eaker Series\, presented by the</span><span> </span><a href="https://ostrom
 workshop.indiana.edu/index.html"><u>Ostrom Workshop</u></a><span> </span><s
 pan>with</span><span> </span><a href="https://kelley.iu.edu/faculty-researc
 h/faculty-directory/profile.html?id=angraymo" target="_blank"><u>Dr. Angie 
 Raymond</u></a><span> </span><span>and the</span><span> </span><a href="htt
 ps://hls.indiana.edu/index.html" target="_blank"><u>Hamilton Lugar School</
 u></a><span> </span><span>with</span><span> </span><a href="https://hls.ind
 iana.edu/faculty/nti-asare-isak.html" target="_blank"><u>Dean Isak Nti Asar
 e</u></a><span>.</span><span> </span>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250321T230945Z
LOCATION:Global and International Studies Building\, 355 Eagleson Ave\, Blo
 omington\, IN 47405\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Tabling for HLS Beyond the Web: Cory Doctorow
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
