 ecember 9th! Ignite your inner fire and flow into your week with <i>Vinyasa
  Heat</i>! This one-hour class is designed to build warmth in your body\, c
 onnect with your breath\, and align mind\, body\, soul\, and spirit. Throug
 h mindful movement and intentional breathing\, we’ll cultivate energy\, str
 ength\, and presence in a supportive community setting. Expect a dynamic se
 quence of poses that will get your heart pumping\, your body moving\, and y
 our spirit grounded. The heat you build will relax tight muscles\, cleanse 
 your system\, and enhance your practice—all leading to a deeply restorative
  Savasana. <b><br></b><br><b>Attend In-Person or via Zoom!</b><ul><li><b>In
 -Person:</b> Space is limited\, so online registration is preferred\, but d
 rop-ins are welcome.</li><li><b>Virtual:</b> Join us live on Zoom and enjoy
