DESCRIPTION:Join us for an insightful presentation on WILPF's (Women's Inte
 rnational League for Peace and Freedom) Global to Local delegation to the 2
 025 Commission on the Status of Women at the United Nations. This year's co
 mmission focused on Beijing+30\, marking three decades since the landmark 1
 995 Beijing Platform for Action. Our presentation will examine both the asp
 irations set forth in Beijing and the current realities facing women worldw
 ide\, analyzing progress toward the Sustainable Development Goals (SDGs) an
 d identifying remaining challenges. Learn how global commitments translate 
 to local action and hear firsthand accounts from our delegation's experienc
 e at this critical international forum for women's rights and gender equali
 ty.
