CREATED:20250313T150702Z
DESCRIPTION:The book explores the loss of collective memory\, the lack of i
 ntergenerational continuity\, and the rupture in our movements that cause u
 s to repeat the same strategic mistakes rather than building off our cumula
 tive knowledge\, wisdom\, and strength.\n\nThe Redbud Nonfiction Reading Gr
 oup is a monthly reading group that actively seeks and explores books that 
 expand horizons and consider new ways of thinking. Meetings generally happe
 n near the end of the month\, on a Sunday\, and discussion is centered arou
 nd the entire text. All are welcome to attend\, regardless of reading progr
 ess\, in a casual environment fostering dialogue and the exchange of ideas.
  If you have a book you would like to suggest and read\, or if you would li
 ke to facilitate a future group\, please feel free to reach out to us at co
